column5: Been having a great season so far.... thought I'd share it   Enjoy!!!  Sorry for the french caption   FISH ON!!!  https://www.facebook.com/jacques.drolet.37/videos/884481774967871/?l=7278972168047950705
Awesome fish pix!  Thanx.  I'm a walleye guy - those are some excellent walleye you have there.
An impressive season and some beautiful meals there.  Nice bass towards the end.
Thanks guys!!!  Sure was fun   Now the wait for the hard water season is on!!!
